"""
    Test that variant libraries load and initialize.
    """
try:
    f = fvs.FVS(variant)
except ImportError:
    pytest.skip('No variant library: {}'.format(variant))
    return None
except:
    raise
assert f.variant == variant
assert not f.fvslib is None
f = None
pytest.mark.parametrize(('variant',), variants)
